OL,5,G0305 Cheap Irish Homes
OL,6,     FMaggie Molloy meets Cork social
OL,7,     Fcare worker Helen Conway, who is
OL,8,     Flooking to leave the suburbs of
OL,9,     FCarrigtwohill and get back to her
OL,10,     Frural roots.
OL,11,G0335 Build Your Own Home
OL,12,     FCian, who was homeless, bought a
OL,13,     Fderelict cottage in Sligo with the
OL,14,     Fhelp of fund raising efforts.
OL,15,     FDetermined to restore the house,
OL,16,     FCian hopes that it will give him a
OL,17,     Fsecure future.
